HEADWORD: Crampfish
<hw>Cramp"fish`</hw> <pr>(kr?mp"f?sh`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The torpedo, or electric ray, the touch of which
gives an electric shock. See <er>Electric fish</er>, and
<er>Torpedo</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

